    "description": "《神奇三国 Kingdoms Hegemony》是一款绝对自由的国战策略游戏，在这里你可以带领军队，参与国家任务，或攻讨地方，或守护己城，带领国家走向强盛，也可以作为军师，运筹帷幄，决胜千里。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350180/extras/679fdbf46a646bbad4442bd4bf804aa2.avif?t=1748623729\" width=616 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>九座真实封地</strong></h2>九座真实存在的国家封地，二十余座诸侯封地，每人都将拥有自己的专属封地！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350180/extras/8da9de2726c37b71a865e404ee564657.avif?t=1748623729\" width=616 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>即时战场策略</strong></h2>完全即时的战场策略，安排武将对线，判定对局变化，抓住战机，一锤落而天下定，还原“狭路相逢勇者胜”的勇将风范。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350180/extras/bb7fba9f872df20b3b8ea20c9ce08f5a.avif?t=1748623729\" width=616 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>即时国战对决</strong></h2>完全即时的国战对决，跑商运粮，调兵遣将，以天下为棋盘，以名将为利刃，攻城拔寨无坚不摧，还原“振长策而御宇内，威加海内”的王者之风。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350180/extras/9cbdfc990fb4d3c72292df63fe4ce4a0.avif?t=1748623729\" width=616 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>公平争霸对战</strong></h2>纯粹策略与操作的比拼，零氪也能打出一片天。是一套连招秒掉对手，还是见招拆招掌控局势，只看您的操作。组合+搭配+策略 = 自己的五虎上将！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2350180/extras/c72c6b6ac14e9b22921d9e763330d710.avif?t=1748623729\" width=616 height=300 /></span>",
